events.name: Maker Faire 2016 Buildup! #1 x Taobao Workshop Session
events.description:
This is the first buildup session for Maker Faire 2016! 

Time schedule:
0900-0920 Introduction/Breakfast
0920-050 "Taobao Training Session" conducted by Melissa Law
1000-1400 Breakout into project groups

We officially close at 9pm. So groups are free to stay around till then!

This event is open for newcomers and all peoples curious about making and Maker Faire 2016. For more details, check out https://makerfairesingapore.com/ We currently have 8 teams (and maybe more!) working on different making projects:

Human Hamster Wheel (Annabelle)
Bucket List Hologram (Mark)
Plastic Injection Machine (Arvin)
Musical Stairs + Shady Umbrella (Saad)
Modular Hovercraft (Kartikey)
Cotton Candy Shooter (Gabriel)
White / Blacksmith (Lev)
Interactive Fabric (Leon)

At last count, we have about 30 volunteers. Contact me at 9633 0898 if you would like to find out more about the projects or check our website at www.onemakergroup.sg for updates.
events.location: OneMaker Group - OMG, 111 Middle Road, #01-02, National Design Centre, Singapore 188969
